{"tid":707796,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【大阪地震】車長拆座椅當逃生梯疏散乘客　原來是阪急電車特別設計","createTime":"2018-06-19T01:32:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-19T02:03:58.000Z","uid":53379,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7176f004da68c7882e6905e9513ca37558bd90b6","tid":707796,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T01:32:53.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【大阪地震】車長拆座椅當逃生梯疏散乘客　原來是阪急電車特別設計 </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180618/s00005/b2c421e5010b07c0a3ec9108c06869bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180618%2Fs00005%2Fb2c421e5010b07c0a3ec9108c06869bb.jpg&h=551bcda5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本大阪今早發生6.1級地震，不少列車受影響停駛。適逢上班上學繁忙時間，工作人員為疏散大批受困乘客，當場拆下列車座椅當逃生梯，讓乘客離開，到安全地方暫避。<br />\n<br />\n日本民眾在社交網站Twitter上載疏散情況，被困乘客有秩序地沿着綠色「逃生梯」走出車廂外。但仔細看，這個協助乘客疏散的逃生梯，卻是列車內的座椅。由於列車出入口與路軌差距太高，工作人員擔心乘客跳下路軌會受傷，遂馬上拆下座椅當逃生梯，讓乘客安全逃生。<br />\n<br />\n可拆除座椅是阪急電車特別設計，當電車在車站與車站間停駛時，民眾爬下電車逃生十分危險，這個設計讓電車在意外發生停駛時，能迅速疏散受困乘客。由於這種情況相當少見，不少人將這一幕拍下在社交網站分享。<br />\n<br />\n（TVBS）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180618/s00005/1529308365252\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180618%2Fs00005%2F1529308365252&d=vqM4mCGDxYbl5X62wekB3gtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=d399fc92\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180618%2Fs00005%2F1529308365252&h=1c41ed5e\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180618/s00005/1529308365252</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34c4d42337bc7e05eaee7f02cd78ceb4800169dd","tid":707796,"uid":886,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T01:36:04.000Z